headline: ADP to Announce Second Quarter Fiscal 2025 Financial Results on January 29, 2025
summary: ADP (Nasdaq: ADP), a leading global provider of Human Capital Management (HCM) solutions, is scheduled to release its financial results for the second fiscal quarter ending December 31, 2024 before the opening of the Nasdaq on Wednesday, January 29, 2025.
